Mafdet's Ledger Houses handle pyramid-provenance attestation for the significant volume of pyramid-era artifacts reaching the harbor through desert trade routes. Sealed Route documentation requirements were developed specifically for funerary consignments and contested inheritance cargo of pyramid-complex origin. Pyramid-provenance stamps require Mafdet clerks trained in the Littoral Branch of Measure Script to cross-reference with the inland charter notation system the original Seal College used for marking authentic containment-related materials. The Jackal Synod's Eclipsed Tongues faction attempts to export through Mafdet materials that would trigger quarantine inspection; Harbor Wardens maintain a running list of Synod-affiliated cargo operators whose consignments receive enhanced inspection.

